  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7110615">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7110615/" class="title-link">我有红颜如秋水</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7110615"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiuyemantan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1621721-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiuyemantan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">秋叶</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-09-25"
      class="main-meta">2014-09-25 18:45:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7110615_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  有人问，男人和女人之间真的有友谊吗？  我现在可以回答：有，秋水和我之间，就是友谊。  我和女子交往，常有非份之想，但我和秋水认识八年，默契十足，却从来没有想过和她有别的发展，这让我也奇怪。我们也曾聊过我们之间有可能吗？答案是我们绝对不可能，做红颜做知己刚刚好...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7110615/#comments">(34回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">106有用 / 9没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7110615_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7110615_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7123070">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7123070/" class="title-link">知性和感性完美结合的秋水</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7123070"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sharptoolbox/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1618689-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sharptoolbox/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">人月神话</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-09"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-09 12:18:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7123070_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  和秋水认识已经差不多快8年的时间了，虽然大家都在深圳，但是从长云离开深圳后实际见面的次数也比原来少了很多。自今年从北京回深圳后，我介绍了一个我的同学给秋水认识，大家聊的也很投缘，得知秋水快要出一本自己的散文集后，我第一时间反映就是早该出了而且会第一时间买一本...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7123070/#comments">(4回应)</a>
