            <div id="review_7123070_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7220459">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7220459/" class="title-link">击穿生来而看不见的桎梏</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7220459"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xseac/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u34037196-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xseac/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小海</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-02"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-02 17:46:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7220459_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  每个人生来就存在于某种桎梏中，它看不见也摸不着。一个人需要花很长的时间去发现它，感觉它，乃至击穿它。  桎梏由许多因素组成。出身，外貌，天赋，性格，也包括成长中的几率事件，还有运气。这些乱序又难以被量化的因素却往往决定了一个人的一生，以至于大多数人的人生轨迹...

