  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7118000/" class="title-link">活在当下</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7118000"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yanshudetudou/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4555019-34.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yanshudetudou/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">鼹鼠的土豆</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-03"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-03 18:34:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7118000_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书是萧秋水用自己的经历写的，诠释了人生成长以及所有的活力都来自于积极的参与和行动，她没有像某些作者一样，鼓励小情绪，鼓励独立，鼓励自由，而是鼓励行动力，执行力。她的观点所谓的小情绪、小孤独，并不值得夸耀，这个世界，想要活得好，用实际行动去争取才是最好的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7118000/#comments">(3回应)</a>
